cz.cuni.mff.kocur.dota2AIFramework

Class App

  • java.lang.Object
    • cz.cuni.mff.kocur.dota2AIFramework.App
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Controllable

    public class App
extends java.lang.Object
implements Controllable
    Class that represents the "main" of this application.
    It has a few states: SETUP, CONFIGURATION, INIT, RUNNING etc., that correspond to the state of the execution.
    There are some functions as start(), debug(), stopServer() etc., that control the application. Theese functions are called from server methods and from buttons on main window.
    This is implemented as singleton. But this as well might have been a static class.
    Author:
    kocur
